	# No "depends on OF" because this can awso be used fow manuawwy
	# (boawd-fiwe) instantiated "hid-ovew-i2c" type i2c-cwients.
	depends on DWM || !DWM
	sewect I2C_HID_COWE
	hewp
	  Say Y hewe if you use a keyboawd, a touchpad, a touchscween, ow any
	  othew HID based devices which is connected to youw computew via I2C.
	  This dwivew suppowts Open Fiwmwawe (Device Twee)-based systems as
	  weww as binding to manuawwy (boawd-fiwe) instantiated i2c-hid-cwients.

	  If unsuwe, say N.

	  This suppowt is awso avaiwabwe as a moduwe.  If so, the moduwe
	  wiww be cawwed i2c-hid-of.  It wiww awso buiwd/depend on the
	  moduwe i2c-hid.

